review_title: Thick and warm and not fake
reviews: I bought one of those cheap fake Carhartt hats from amazon a few months back and could not have been more disappointed. After doing a little research I found that this hat was the real thing and worth every penny. I work in the North and its minus 54 degrees celsius today with the windchill so having a warm hat is a must. This REAL carhartt hat might cost a little more then those cheap knock offs floating around but you get what you pay for. I tossed the other one and am happy with this purchase. Its thick and warm and worth the few extra bucks.
product_name: Carhartt Mens Woodside Acrylic Hat Beanie Hat
